en_486302_0	One more full-day workshop, conducted by Ven Diyasenpura Wimala Thero, the resident monk at Kanduboda Bavunseth Vipassana Bhavana Centre on Tuesday (17) provided meditation training for a group of 89 Army personnel including four Officers.
en_486302_1	Directorate of Psychological Operations instrumental in providing these spiritual healing practices has specially designed the ‘Lakviru Spiritual Meditation Programme’ for the benefit of Army personnel on the guidelines given by the Director of Psychological Operations.
